{{Infobox Berry |name = Wacan |image = [[File:Wacan.png]] |caption = Energy from lightning strikes is drawn into the plant, making the Berries grow big and rich. The same energy promotes the growth of nearby Berries. |growtime = 30m 0s |harvest = 2 berries |replant = 5% |points = 250 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 15 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 10 }} '''Wacan''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding an empty plot with at least 1 [[Iapapa]], at least 1 [[Qualot]], at least 1 [[Pinap]] and at least 1 [[Grepa]].
